skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fruit cups
des:
Useful tools and silly pranks created by members of the FC community, for members of the FC community.

Many different global timers can be set by your assistant and they will be announced in Discord for everyone to hear.

Must be a member of the official FC discord for this to be any fun. This skill contains humour, satire and parodies, please do not be alarmed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
